title: This Month's GTA+ Benefits
headline: This Month's GTA+ Benefits
subtitle: GTA+
content:
In addition to the recurring monthly GTA$500,000 deposited directly into your Maze Bank account, GTA+ Members who've signed up for this month (January 9 - February 5) will also receive:

— The new Vapid Dominator GT (Muscle)
— 2X GTA$ and RP on Terrorbyte Client Jobs
— 40% off Arcade Properties and their Upgrades and Modifications
— And more

Membership automatically renews monthly, cancel anytime. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
